        "bodyHtml": "<p>“Let’s discover the deeper purpose behind our work by asking why it truly matters.”</p>\n<p>Key questions: What do you do when working on [X]? Why is that important to you? Why does that matter? Keep asking, “Why? Why? Why?” up to nine times or until participants can go no deeper because they have reached the fundamental purpose for this work.</p>"
