        "label": "4. Group Configuration",
        "subtitle": "How people are arranged (alone, small groups, or all together) and how this shifts during the activity.",
        "bodyHtml": "<ul>\n<li>Pairs for interviews</li>\n<li>Optional: Groups of four for sharing (2-4-All)</li>\n<li>Whole group for harvest</li>\n</ul>"
