        "label": "5. Sequence & Timing",
        "subtitle": "The step-by-step flow of the activity and the time given to each step to keep energy and focus.",
        "bodyHtml": "<ol>\n<li>Each person in a pair is interviewed by their partner for 5 minutes. Starting with “What do you do when working on ____?” the interviewer gently seeks a deeper answer by repeating the query: “Why is that important to you?” Switch roles after 5 minutes. (10 min)</li>\n<li>Each pair shares the experience and insights with another pair in a foursome. Compare and notice patterns (5 min)</li>\n<li>Invite the whole group to reflect by asking, “How do our purposes influence the next steps we take?” (5 min)</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Total time: 20 minutes</p>"
